Name: SHADE The Border Collie Flycatcher
About the game: SHADE The Border Collie Flycatcher is an exciting point and shoot game that challenges players to catch as many flies as possible. With simple and intuitive gameplay and colorful graphics, players of all ages can enjoy this fun and engaging game. Please note that the game cannot be paused, so make sure you have uninterrupted playtime to achieve your highest score. Join Shade on this thrilling adventure and test your reflexes and precision in a fast-paced game of flycatching!
